<main role="main" aria-label="Coffee & Connections Press Kit">
<section class="press-intro">
  <div class="text-block">
    <h2>What if a cup of coffee could save someone's life?</h2>
    <p class="tagline">A Cup of Coffee <strong>CAN</strong> Save a Life.</p>
    <p>“Some of life’s most healing moments happen… when someone simply says, ‘Stay awhile.’”</p>
    <p>This short video was created by our co-founder, <strong>Marylou Culpepper</strong>, a survivor whose story is woven into every frame. Using humble art and honest narration, it introduces the vision behind Coffee & Connections—a space where strangers become family, and recovery begins with one open seat.</p>
    <p>It’s not just about coffee. It’s about <strong>connection that doesn’t come with conditions</strong>. And <strong>belonging that doesn’t ask for explanation</strong>.</p>
    <blockquote>“We didn’t build this café to fix people. We built it to hold them. Because we’ve been there too.”<br>— <strong>Anthony Sorensen</strong>, Founder</blockquote>
    <blockquote>“No one has to heal alone or feel shamed asking for help. This café will make sure of that.”<br>— <strong>Marylou Culpepper</strong>, Co-Founder</blockquote>
    <blockquote>“Moving forward doesn’t erase the weight—it reshapes it.”<br>— <strong>Don Markland</strong></blockquote>
    <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1KcrclHJNfFTYyhK7eq2EOEsMFoJ1EWdN/view?usp=drive_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Watch Coffee & Connections video on Google Drive">🎥 Watch the video on Google Drive</a>
  </div>
</section>
     
